<item>
            <title>[LU-18814] improve ha.sh to run extra prog and execute NLOOPS mpi workloads</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18814</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch adds the the following abilities to ha.sh:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;execute the workload the specified number of times (NLOOPS) instead of execution them during the test duration set;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;execute the mpi EXTRAPROG in addition to allowed now IOR, mdtest and simul;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;execute more mpi instances than the number of clients in case if NLOOPS set.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
